Homepage: https://github.com/onyxdigitaldev/tp-fanctl
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: tp-fanctl
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3 (>= 3.10), thinkfan
Recommends: python3-gi, gir1.2-appindicator3-0.1
Description: Adaptive fan controller for ThinkPad laptops
 Automatically switches between quiet and gaming fan profiles based on
 CPU load. Built on top of thinkfan with hysteresis to prevent thrashing.
 .
 Features:
  - Asymmetric thresholds: fast ramp-up (12s), slow cooldown (30s)
  - System tray applet with manual override
  - Profile switching via SIGHUP (no fan reset)
  - Clean shutdown restores BIOS fan control
